    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/8388ec3689f8ded61a13fdf8d57588ec.avif?t=1767863930\" width=610 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/a14bee39c8a3e58304f97702a7961ad4.avif?t=1767863930\" width=610 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/ab821bf65caa63f94a427f51594a1f93.webp?t=1767863930\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/41d4ada492acafabb7c0500381631af1.poster.avif?t=1767863930\" width=609 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/41d4ada492acafabb7c0500381631af1.webm?t=1767863930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《BEAST》是一款火爆异常的3v3多人英雄射击游戏。装备强力机甲，畅享超快节奏和动感元素，制霸每一场对战！选择最喜爱的角色，即刻投身快节奏的刺激游戏，随时随地享受轻松乐趣。《BEAST》为广大玩家打造轻松惬意的游戏体验，不设门槛，即点即玩，令人大呼过瘾！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/bc973ad84e22e5c4e135a2659de1946e.webp?t=1767863930\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/8e0a110cd9494b7182974d5a4acbc90e.poster.avif?t=1767863930\" width=609 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/8e0a110cd9494b7182974d5a4acbc90e.webm?t=1767863930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验创造性的双形态玩法系统，在强力的MECHA机甲和敏捷的PET兽驭之间无缝切换，前者可以发挥强大力量，后者则可运用灵活战术。每种形态均自带独特技能，为每场对决带来变数和深度！依靠无缝切换和灵活策略来扭转战局吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/ccac8185872f43eb349725b43619b357.webp?t=1767863930\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/fc42280e00a38098aae6324c3201677d.poster.avif?t=1767863930\" width=609 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/fc42280e00a38098aae6324c3201677d.webm?t=1767863930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在独一无二的英雄阵容中挑选勇士出战，每一位英雄都有自己的特殊能力和玩法。无论你喜欢重火力、快速打击还是战略防御，总有一款英雄适合你的游玩风格，战斗的层次也将得到拓展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/d8ff50de35e6fbc1d96894bcd792c26e.webp?t=1767863930\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/d4237f11051447767485b1ea858dfc25.poster.avif?t=1767863930\" width=609 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/d4237f11051447767485b1ea858dfc25.webm?t=1767863930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实力比付费更重要！《BEAST》不存在微交易，并承诺打造公正而平衡游戏的环境，能力和成就才是变强的关键。用自己的技巧、策略以及团队精神赢得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/ec0650f2df59b83ccc893c075eda2dd9.webp?t=1767863930\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/c07c66fafc62d4ec79a6c4cd369d064b.poster.avif?t=1767863930\" width=609 height=335 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239670/extras/c07c66fafc62d4ec79a6c4cd369d064b.webm?t=1767863930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持激动人心的体验，探索多种游戏模式，沉浸在丰富的单人冒险中。 试验不同的英雄协同作战，瞬间切换至BEAST形态，探索主宰竞技场的最佳策略。 无论是在多人战斗中测试技能，还是在单人模式下揭开每位英雄的故事，BEAST都提供无限玩法！</p>",
